                    <li><strong>Supporting the Local Economy</strong> &ndash; When you choose a local company like Griffin Quartz, your investment stays within the community, supporting local jobs and the regional economy.</li>
                    <li><strong>Understanding Regional Trends</strong> &ndash; A local fabricator understands the design preferences, architectural styles, and environmental conditions specific to South Florida, ensuring your countertops are both beautiful and built for the local climate.</li>
